In article <ZA0ytL9.wschwartau@delphi.com> wschwartau@delphi.com writes:
> Can you point me to the existing work?  I am only familiar with the basic
> stuff from Sci Amer.
> Thanks
> Winn

Gilles Brassard, Charles Bennet, Claude Crepeau and others have
published a lot about the subject.  The easiest to find are the Crypto
and EuroCrypt conference proceedings.  They are published by
Springer-Verlag as part of the collection Advances in Cryptology.
Look at the 1984 to 1993 editions.

Otherwise, Charles Bennet and David Deutch have also published in
Physical Review.

I can probably give more precise references if given a more narrow
search criteria.
